@node "BRIEF" "Brief Description of Pictures"
@next "AUTHOR"
@prev "MAIN"

This is a collection of Photographs of the World of Amiga show 1997 which
have been scanned and placed on Aminet.  

The Pictures are as follows:

@{b}AISTAND.IFFC@{ub}   Is a picture of the Amiga International Stand.
                       It is @{i}154058@{ui} bytes in size.

@{b}AMFORMAT.IFFC@{ub}  Is a picture of the Amiga Format Stand.
                       It is @{i}153624@{ui} bytes in size.

@{b}DIGITA.IFFC@{ub}    Is a picture of the Digita Stand.
                       It is @{i}158420@{ui} bytes in size.

@{b}HIQ.IFFC@{ub}       Is a picture of a computer running the Siamese System
                       It is @{i}161334@{ui} bytes in size.

@{b}MICRONIK.IFFC@{ub}  Is a picture of a Micronik Tower system.
                       It is @{i}125544@{ui} bytes in size.

@{b}PLEASENCE.IFFC@{ub} Is a picture of David near the Power Computing Stand.
                       It is @{i}154332@{ui} bytes in size.
                       My apologies if I have spelt his surname incorrectly.
@endnode
@node "AUTHOR" "Who took the Photos?"
@prev "BRIEF"
